	<dita:topic xmlns="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="Rosetta_emph-Chof-remotelink-LxAdv-omit_tag">
    <title><sourcexml>remotelink/emph</sourcexml> to <sourcexml>emph</sourcexml> tag omitted <lnpid>id-CCCC-10315</lnpid></title>    
<body>
	<section>
		<title>Instructions <i>[common element]</i></title>
	    
	    <p>
                <b>When <sourcexml>emph</sourcexml> is inside the <sourcexml>remotelink</sourcexml>
                    and remotelink markup comes with attributes <sourcexml>[@href]</sourcexml> and
                        <sourcexml>[@hrefclass]</sourcexml> in source document then conversion need
                    to omit <sourcexml>emph</sourcexml> start and end tag in target
                    conversion.</b></p>
	    <note>In this case, suppress the <sourcexml>emph</sourcexml> from target conversion and presentation stylesheet will handle formatting or desired styling.</note>
	</section>
    
	    <example>
	        <title>Source XML</title>
	        <codeblock>

&lt;remotelink href="tta.ac.nz" hrefclass="http"&gt;
    &lt;emph typestyle="it"&gt;http://tta.ac.nz&lt;/emph&gt;
&lt;/remotelink&gt;

	</codeblock>
	    </example>
	    
	    <example>
	        <title>Target XML</title>
	        <codeblock>

&lt;url normval="http://tta.ac.nz"&gt;http://tta.ac.nz&lt;/url&gt;

	</codeblock>
	    </example>
    
